// Wave 2 piece N: LifeSteal E2E demo. Caster gains a 5-second window
// during which 50% of damage they deal heals them back. Lowers to
// AbilityProgram { effects: [EffectOp::LifeSteal{duration_ticks: 50,
// fraction_q8: 128}] }. The .sim verb writes the lifesteal SoA fields
// (frac_q8 = 128 for 50%, expires_at = world.tick + 50); ApplyDamage
// reads source's lifesteal state per Damaged event and emits Healed
// for the source if the window is active. ApplyHeal drains the
// resulting Healed event into source.hp.

ability Vampirize {
    target: self
    cooldown: 8s

    lifesteal 0.5 5s
}
